How to start the service:

1. copy the settings
  1.1. local_settings:
    - obtain the settings from the secret manager
    - copy it to mediacms/deploy/docker/local_settings.py
  1.2. .env:
    - obtain the .env from the secret manager
    - place it under mediacms/

2. (first time) setup SAML configs
  2.1 Add identity provider settings (example in secret manager)
  2.2 run `bash fix_socialapp_settings.sh` to actually place the config into socialapp.settings
    - fail running this script will face the missing 'idp' error when accessing https://tube.corp.foundi.info/accounts/saml/foundi-info/metadata

3. start the service
  2.1 `bash start.sh`
